txt.en: 'You have no doubt felt the size of the Eastemnet. Travel can take days if you do not have an able-bodied horse to take you across the plains. Stables connect our towns and allow for travel. If we are to join the trade networks within the eastern plains, we must rebuild our stable.'
'Hytbold is one step closer to being rebuilt and restored.'
There is much work to do to rebuild the town of Hytbold.
